# Package-local scratch directory — debug scripts, intermediate
# captures, and probe output land here so they don't pollute the
# repository-wide `.tmp-output/`. Per AGENTS.md, .tmp scripts are
# meant to be ephemeral; promote anything worth keeping into a
# proper spec under `spec/cases/<name>/` instead.
.tmp/

# Full-page fixtures and their `.fig` snapshots. The extractor
# inlines every image / font / mask asset as a `data:` URL by
# design, so a `body`-rooted snapshot of a real page weighs tens
# to hundreds of MB and rotates daily. Each `cases-fullpage/<case>/`
# ships an `extract.sh` so a developer can regenerate locally; we
# never commit the materialised fixture or snapshot.
spec/cases-fullpage/*/fixture.html
spec/cases-fullpage/*/snapshot.fig

# Snapshot fig dumps from partial-selector cases — also produced
# by spec runs (via runHtmlCase's `dumpFigTo`) and not source of
# truth for any assertion.
spec/cases/*/snapshot.fig
